
Resource naming

<BU>-Business unit or company-contoso, fin, hr
<MGMT>-Management scope / service domain-it, ops, sec
<ENV>-Environment-dev, test, qa, prod
<REG>-Azure Region short code-Eastus2, westeurope
<RTYPE>-Azure resource type abbreviation-vm, rg, vnet, stg
<APP/TIER>-Application, project, or tier-appapi, backend, db
<NNN>-Instance or sequence number-001, 002

Resource Tagging

BusinessUnit-Owner business unit or company-Contoso
MgmtScope-Management or operational domain-IT, Security
Env-Deployment environment-Prod, Dev, Test
CostCenter-Chargeback / billing identifier-CC12345
ProductOwner-Stakeholder or team responsible-AppPlatformTeam
DataSensitivity-Data classification for compliance-Confidential, Public
CreatedBy-who-email
Backup Required-Yes or No-Y/N
